WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.800
This is what happens after a prospective client submits an IntakeBrief form.

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:15.600
They enter a short, non-confidential description and accept the required notices.

00:00:15.600 --> 00:00:24.700
The lead reaches the firm, the likely matter is identified, and the client gets a response that matches the inquiry.

00:00:24.700 --> 00:00:36.000
The client selects an open consultation time. IntakeBrief holds it while Stripe hosts the fifty-dollar test checkout.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:44.800
After payment, the browser waits for signed webhook verification.

00:00:44.800 --> 00:00:51.400
The confirmation email closes the loop: qualified lead, scheduled consultation, and verified deposit.
